<!-- 新增/编辑课程：时间、学生、时长；保存时触发自动顺延与冲突检测 -->
<view class="page-root {{ isBoss ? 'boss-ui' : '' }}">
  <!-- boss 主题 -->
  <app-background />
  <view class="page-wrap">
  <view class="edit-hero glass-card">
    <view class="ios-section-title">{{ isEdit ? '编辑课程' : '新增课程' }}</view>
    <view class="ios-section-subtitle">学生与课时单价均以「学生名单」为准；此处仅展示，改价请去名单。</view>
  </view>
  <view class="orphan-hint glass-card" wx:if="{{ orphanStudentName }}">
    <text class="orphan-hint-text">原课程学生「{{ orphanStudentName }}」已不在当前名单中，请从下方重新选择学生后再保存。</text>
  </view>
  <view class="empty-roster-hint glass-card" wx:if="{{ !hasStudents }}">
    <text class="empty-roster-text">还没有学生，请先到「设置 → 学生名单」添加学生，再回来排课。</text>
    <view class="glass-btn glass-btn-primary empty-roster-btn" bindtap="onOpenStudents">去添加学生</view>
  </view>
  <view class="form glass-card">
    <view class="row">
      <text class="label">日期</text>
      <text class="value">{{ dateDisplay }}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <text class="label">开始时间</text>
      <picker mode="time" value="{{ startTime }}" bindchange="onStartTimeChange">
        <view class="picker-val">{{ startTime || '选择时间' }}</view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class="row row--duration">
      <text class="label">时长（分钟）</text>
      <view class="duration-block">
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{ durationOptions }}" value="{{ durationIndex }}" bindchange="onDurationChange">
          <view class="picker-val">{{ durationOptions[durationIndex] }}分钟</view>
        </picker>
        <view class="duration-custom-wrap">
          <input
            class="duration-custom-input"
            type="number"
            value="{{ customDurationDraft }}"
            placeholder="自定义分钟数"
            placeholder-class="student-search-placeholder"
            confirm-type="done"
            bindinput="onCustomDurationInput"
            bindblur="onCustomDurationConfirm"
            bindconfirm="onCustomDurationConfirm"
          />
          <view class="glass-btn duration-custom-btn" bindtap="onCustomDurationConfirm">应用</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="row row--student">
      <text class="label">学生</text>
      <view class="student-block">
        <picker wx:if="{{ hasStudents }}" mode="selector" range="{{ studentPickerOptions }}" range-key="label" value="{{ studentPickerIndex }}" bindchange="onStudentPickerChange">
          <view class="picker-val">{{ studentPickerOptions.length ? studentPickerOptions[studentPickerIndex].label : '加载中…' }}</view>
        </picker>
        <text wx:else class="picker-val picker-val--disabled">请先在下方或设置中添加学生</text>
        <block wx:if="{{ hasStudents }}">
          <text class="student-search-hint text-caption">或输入姓名查找</text>
          <!-- 输入框放在不透明容器内，避免在 glass-card（backdrop-filter）内直接渲染导致真机文字重叠/镜像 -->
          <view class="student-search-input-wrap">
            <input
              class="student-search-input"
              type="text"
              value="{{ studentSearchQuery }}"
              placeholder="输入姓名筛选"
              placeholder-class="student-search-placeholder"
              confirm-type="search"
              bindinput="onStudentSearchInput"
            />
          </view>
          <view class="student-suggest" wx:if="{{ studentSuggestList.length }}">
            <view
              class="student-suggest-item"
              wx:for="{{ studentSuggestList }}"
              wx:key="id"
              data-id="{{ item.id }}"
              catchtap="onPickStudentFromSuggest"
            >
              <text class="student-suggest-name">{{ item.name }}</text>
            </view>
          </view>
          <text wx:if="{{ studentSearchQuery && !studentSuggestList.length }}" class="student-no-match text-caption">无匹配，请换关键词或从上方列表选择</text>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="row row--price">
      <view class="label-col">
        <text class="label">该学生单价</text>
        <text class="price-footnote text-caption">改价请去「学生名单」</text>
      </view>
      <view class="price-display-col">
        <text class="value price-readonly">{{ studentPriceLine }}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="row row--price">
      <view class="label-col">
        <text class="label">该学生分成</text>
        <text class="price-footnote text-caption">改比例请去「学生名单」</text>
      </view>
      <view class="price-display-col">
        <text class="value price-readonly">{{ studentShareLine }}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <text class="label">上课提醒</text>
      <picker mode="selector" range="{{ reminderOptions }}" range-key="label" value="{{ reminderIndex }}" bindchange="onReminderChange">
        <view class="picker-val">{{ reminderOptions[reminderIndex].label }}</view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class="row row--note">
      <text class="label">备注</text>
      <view class="note-block">
        <!-- 不透明底 + 独立层，规避 glass-card 模糊合成层上原生 input 的渲染异常 -->
        <view class="note-input-wrap">
          <input
            class="note-input"
            type="text"
            value="{{ note }}"
            placeholder="如：下午、待定、试课（仅自己可见）"
            placeholder-class="student-search-placeholder"
            maxlength="30"
            bindinput="onNoteInput"
          />
        </view>
        <text class="note-hint text-caption">给这节课加个小提醒，不影响上课时间</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" wx:if="{{ isEdit }}">
      <text class="label">复制到其他日期</text>
      <picker mode="date" start="{{ todayStr }}" bindchange="onCopyToOtherDate">
        <view class="link-btn">选择日期并复制</view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class="row nav-row" bindtap="onOpenStudents">
      <text class="label">学生名单</text>
      <text class="link-btn">添加 / 改单价 / 区分色</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="btn-wrap">
    <view class="glass-btn glass-btn-primary save-btn" bindtap="onSave">保存</view>
    <view class="glass-btn cancel-btn" wx:if="{{ isEdit }}" bindtap="onDelete">{{ isFinished ? '删除课程' : '取消课程' }}</view>
  </view>

  <ios-modal
    show="{{ modalShow }}"
    title="{{ modalTitle }}"
    content="{{ modalContent }}"
    confirmText="{{ modalConfirmText }}"
    cancelText="{{ modalCancelText }}"
    showCancel="{{ modalShowCancel }}"
    bind:confirm="onModalConfirm"
    bind:cancel="onModalCancel"
  />
  </view>
</view>
